{"prompt": "Generate a website for a edtech platform. The website should be futuristic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>EdTech Futura</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #ff0000;\n            --secondary-color: #330000;\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #0a0a0a;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            height: 100vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 4em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n\n        .features {\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .features h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 50px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 40px;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--brand-color);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\n        }\n\n        .footer {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);\n        }\n\n        .footer a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 10px;\n        }\n\n        .footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n\n        /* Animated background elements */\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: -50%;\n            left: -50%;\n            width: 200%;\n            height: 200%;\n            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05) 20%, transparent 40%);\n            animation: rotate 15s linear infinite;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        .hero::after {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: -50%;\n            left: -50%;\n            width: 200%;\n            height: 200%;\n            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.03) 20%, transparent 40%);\n            animation: rotate 20s linear infinite reverse;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes rotate {\n            from {\n                transform: rotate(0deg);\n            }\n            to {\n                transform: rotate(360deg);\n            }\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 3em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            .features h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .feature-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Ignite Your Future</h1>\n        <p>Experience the next generation of learning with AI-powered personalized education and immersive digital experiences.</p>\n        <a href=\"#features\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Now</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"features\" class=\"features\">\n        <h2>Cutting-Edge Learning Features</h2>\n        <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Personalized AI Tutors</h3>\n                <p>Get one-on-one guidance from intelligent tutors that adapt to your unique learning style and pace.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Immersive VR Labs</h3>\n                <p>Step into virtual reality environments for hands-on experiments and simulations like never before.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Global Collaboration</h3>\n                <p>Connect and learn with students and educators from around the world in real-time.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Skill Tracking & Analytics</h3>\n                <p>Monitor your progress with advanced analytics and identify areas for growth.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer class=\"footer\">\n        <p>&copy; 2042 EdTech Futura. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>\n            <a href=\"#\">Privacy Policy</a> |\n            <a href=\"#\">Terms of Service</a> |\n            <a href=\"#\">Contact Us</a>\n        </p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Optional: Add some subtle JavaScript interactions if needed later\n        // For this example, the focus is on CSS animations for a futuristic feel.\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}